{"tid":1902774,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各位冷氣軍師唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2020-02-28T14:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T12:00:38.000Z","uid":264429,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"da23fd29b8b441ed74e1f1272645e070ad478344","tid":1902774,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"不論你平時係冷氣軍師定係暖爐軍師都好<br />\n<br />\n今次，我歡迎你地每一位冷/暖氣軍師，我地大家一齊涼住冷氣抗爭，響屋企 un 住腳抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n只要你參與民間集會團隊嘅 「疫症當前 警暴蔓延」831半周年網上集會<br />\n就可以一次過滿足哂：足不出戶涼住冷氣，食住薯片，飲住啤酒抗爭呢三個願望啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個可能係香港抗爭史上最舒服嘅群眾活動，<br />\n而家有個咁好嘅機會，你唔係唔參與呀？<br />\n<br />\n日期：2月29日<br />\n時間：7pm-9pm<br />\n直播媒體：<br />\n民間集會團隊FACEBOOK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=f2d54f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\n民間集會團隊YouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCU-tzwz-e8ynKgYR-r2AAzQ/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCU-tzwz-e8ynKgYR-r2AAzQ%2Ffeatured&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=8eed74ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCU-tzwz-e8ynKgYR-r2AAzQ/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n至於本身都會出去嘅手足，唔需要我多講啦，大家自然會識得點做啦<br />\n聽晚見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3dGD8z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3dGD8z.jpg&h=f4be8c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pcs0UGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcs0UGU.jpg&h=423a0fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxOGD8z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxOGD8z.jpg&h=5929aabc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3018a6ac711c23d14ad5166a51c25a7ca6097887","tid":1902774,"uid":264429,"like":1,"disl